S . Korea ' s NLCF buys 37 , 500 tonnes of Chinese corn . South Korea ' s National Livestock Cooperatives Federation ( NLCF ) bought 37 , 500 tonnes of Chinese corn on Saturday at $ 141 . 90 a tonne C & F , an official at the association said on Monday . He said the purchase was made in three 12 , 500 - tonne cargoes from Toepfer through private negotiation . Arrival for the first cargo was set by April 25 , the second by May 5 and the third by May 30 to the port of Kunsan . - - Seoul Newsroom ( 822 ) 727 5651 
